data.description: SELLER NOW OFFERING $2K ALLOWANCE FOR FLOORING OR CLOSING COSTS! Warm your bones in this 1200 gal Swim Spa that the seller paid almost $20K to have installed! Well maintained home with MANY costly updates done within the last five years to include Triple pane windows throughout, gutters all the way around, 550 gal rain barrel for rain capture, upgraded electrical to 200 amp, 6' cedar fence, gas insert with remote in fireplace, dishwasher and refrigerator that conveys, built in oven, microwave, workshop, raised bed garden, sprinkler system, gas water heater, garage door opener, 15 inches of insulation in attic, and St. Augustine sod. Don't miss out on this great home in desired neighborhood...close to CHS!
